		<item>
		<title>入冬吃什么蔬菜最好（入冬后要吃的4种水果）</title>
		<link>https://www.huacao77.com/5408.html</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[广少, 腹肌之广]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Mon, 17 Jul 2023 11:35:44 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[水果百科]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[入冬]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[生津]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[金桔]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.huacao77.com/?p=5408</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[入冬后天气由凉转寒，空气也变得非常干燥，大家在进补储备能量的同时，也要多吃应季水果滋阴润燥，维持体内营养均衡， [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">入冬后</span></strong>天气<strong style="color: blue;">由凉转寒</strong>，<strong style="color: blue;">空气也变得非常干燥</strong>，大家在进补储备能量的同时，也<strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">要多吃应季水果滋阴润燥，维持体内营养均衡，防止上火</span></strong>。</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/ca6932c38ecf9558d46c36b63b868f1d.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">油炸鹰嘴豆Fried chickpeas</p>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">不要单纯地以为冬季吃<strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">水果</span></strong>只是为了<strong style="color: blue;">补充水分和维生素</strong>，它能<strong style="color: blue;">够弥补肉食和蔬菜的不足，起到<span style="color: green;">开胃生津</span>、<span style="color: green;">化痰止咳</span>、<span style="color: green;">润肺生津</span>、<span style="color: green;">美容养颜</span>等作用</strong>。下面，我就给大家推荐<strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">4种冬季必吃的水果</span></strong>，<strong style="color: blue;">入冬后，有钱没钱都要吃，润肺降燥补维C，应季而食更养人！</strong></p>
    <h1 style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;">一、金桔</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">开胃生津</strong>、<strong style="color: blue;">润喉护嗓</strong>、<strong style="color: blue;">抗寒防感冒</strong></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/806a17d15cc47021766e376304cb28a0.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">推荐做法：<span style="color: green;">【糖渍金桔】</span></strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">1.</strong>金桔500克，用淡盐水浸泡洗干净放入锅中，加入500克冰糖，再倒入适量的清水没过金桔，开大火把冰糖煮化。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">2.</strong>然后转为小火继续煮30分钟，时不时搅拌让金桔均匀受热。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">3.</strong>30分钟以后当水分剩余一小部分的时候转大火收汁，直至糖水收到粘稠就可以关火了，晾凉以后装在罐子里，随时吃随时取，当茶点正合适。</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/f15730348d119e7fb9a95162401256c0.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <h1 style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;">二、梨</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">清热化痰</strong>、<strong style="color: blue;">润肺止咳</strong>、<strong style="color: blue;">滋养肠胃</strong></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/33e50cabfc34248e37f78879ff58a2ee.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">推荐做法：<span style="color: green;">【雪梨银耳羹】</span></strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">1.</strong>泡发的银耳，剪去黄色的硬根、撕成小块；梨子去核、切成片；碗中放入20克冰糖，再舀进去几勺桂花酱，另外准备半碗米酒备用。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">2.</strong>锅内多烧一些水，凉水放入银耳慢慢煮，水烧开以后倒入雪梨、冰糖和桂花，继续煮至沸腾，然后转为小火炖煮1个小时，小火慢煨才能充分炖出银耳的胶原。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">3.</strong>一个小时以后银耳羹已经起黏 ，色泽晶莹，这个时候我们把米酒倒进去，让酒糟的香气和银耳羹充分融合，温润滋补的银耳羹就能食用了。</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/94a2477e546fb7a06de34b9a12bccf2a.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <h1 style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;">三、柚子</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">润肺健脾</strong>、<strong style="color: blue;">消食化积</strong>、<strong style="color: blue;">补水润肤</strong></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/8ac125b1584347c71a4318ce3b2e14aa.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">推荐做法：<span style="color: green;">【蜂蜜柚子茶】</span></strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">1.</strong>把柚子用食盐反复搓洗几遍，去除柚子皮上的杂质和果蜡，然后冲洗干净，把柚子的黄皮刮下来切成细丝，不要带里面的海绵瓤，不然会有苦味；果肉去皮、把肉掰成块；另外准备适量的冰糖备用。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">2.</strong>锅里烧水，放入柚子皮汆煮一下、去除苦涩味，开锅以后倒出来用清水冲洗干净、控水备用。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">3.</strong>锅内再烧水，大火烧开以后放入果肉、果皮以及冰糖，大火把冰糖熬化、果肉熬散。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">4.</strong>然后转小火经常搅拌，一直熬至水分全部蒸发，呈现出果泥状就可以了，晾凉以后倒在保鲜盒中，加入蜂蜜搅拌均匀，天然无添加的蜂蜜柚子茶，三天两头冲一杯，补水补维C 。</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/7579f21dfd492aeeffddc3d022db0b22.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <h1 style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;">四、苹果</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">开胃生津</strong>、<strong style="color: blue;">润肺平肝</strong>、<strong style="color: blue;">美容养颜</strong></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="///static.zixunkankan.xyz/image628/tree_image/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/7ff08bb51c5938042ca397da54b33699.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">推荐做法：<span style="color: green;">【苹果煎饼】</span></strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">1.</strong>苹果两个削净外皮，其中一个的苹果切成小粒，加入白糖20克，面粉100克，用力揉成苹果面团。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">2.</strong>另一个苹果也切成小粒，放入锅中翻炒1分钟，苹果出汁以后淋入少许水淀粉增加苹果粒的粘性，翻匀后盛出，做苹果馅心。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">3.</strong>取适量的苹果面团压扁，放入一勺苹果馅，把开口收紧，表面沾满芝麻后压扁，做成苹果饼的生坯。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">4.</strong>电饼铛烧热均匀刷上油，把饼坯依次放入锅中，盖上锅盖烙3分钟，饼周围变色以后在上面淋一层植物油，锁住饼内部的水分，然后翻过来再烙2分钟，饼两面都呈金黄色时即可出锅，软糯香甜的苹果煎饼就做好了。</p>
